title: Next project to add to list of options
body:
Recently, BAYC was voted to be part of our list of options and eventually went on to be the highest voted option to be the community's next purchase. 

Now, we would like to hear your opinion again on the next project to be part of our options to purchase.

The projects are:

1. Anonymice
2. Cryptoadz
3. Cyberkongz
4. Creature World
5. 0n1 Force
6. MAYC
7. Bored Ape Chemistry Club
8. World of Women
9. Vee Friends
10. The Doge Pound
11. Sneaky Vampire Syndicate
12. GalacticApes
